# Landing Sections

- Export named function components: `Hero`, `Features`, etc.
- Use `"use client"` only when hooks, motion, or event handlers are needed
- Spacing: `py-24 md:py-32`, container `mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 md:px-6`
- Headings: `text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight`
- Cards: `.glass` utility from globals.css for glassmorphism
- Import copy from `@/content/ru`
- Framer Motion: `whileInView`, `viewport={{ once: true, margin: "-80px" }}`
